{"word":"H7533 - רָצַץ - râtsats - raw-tsats' - Break","slug":"H7533","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָצַץ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>râtsats"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>raw-tsats'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Break"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E8;&#x05E6;&#x05E5; - ra&#x0302;tsats</b> - <i>raw-tsats'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>crack</i> in pieces, literally or figuratively: - break, bruise, crush, discourage, oppress, struggle together."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4835\">H4835</a>, <a href=\"#/H7518\">H7518</a>"}]}